   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Give the learning power of play to 1000&apos;s of kids</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Our project focuses on engaging 1000&apos;s children, from 30 primary schools across the Pafuri Node of the Great Limpopo Transfrontier Conservation Area in Southern Africa. By engaging children through soccer we are able to harness their energy, create safe spaces to allow them to discuss and learn how to tackle social issues affecting them and the environments in which they grow up in, from HIV, gender equality, poaching and substance abuse.</narrative>
  </description>
